Got the AM Kinda working tonight in a rush, but at 22 seconds you can hear  
"Drats, Can You Hear Me?".  Definitely a rush job throwing this box  
together and it needs some work, but i still got something intelligible from the  
first run.  I think changing parts constantly is confusing them and  me.
 
-Steve H.
